The '''Ingoians''' were the colonists who inhabited [[Ingo/Legends|Ingo]], a [[Planet/Legends|planet]] which lacked native [[Sentience/Legends|sentients]]. Ingoians included a large number of [[Species/Legends|species]], including [[Human/Legends|Humans]].

